  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You must have formed a Blood Contract with a Sage Tribe, such as one found in the <strong>Summoning Jutsu</strong> section found at the end of the <strong>Ninjutsu</strong> chapter in order to successfully cast this jutsu. If a creature refuses or cannot be summoned, You spend chakra according to the rank this jutsu was cast.</p><p>It appears where the user designates and can act as a Bonus Action on the user's turn, on the user's initiative order. You can communicate with the creature and it will listen to you and only you in combat. You can direct it to perform the following actions: Attack (Unarmed, Weapon, or Jutsu), Dodge, and Help. The creature can perform an Action and Move. The summoned creature must remain within 120 feet of the summoner. All sage creatures can speak common.</p><p><strong>At Higher Ranks</strong>:</p><p>For each rank you cast this jutsu above D-Rank, you summon a corresponding creature equal in level and rank to the Rank used upon activation.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
